descriptionHtml:
What to you need for a cool S/M-Party? Yes, a lot of sexy housecarls (not finished yet), sexy underwear and perhaps: 

[IMG]http://static.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/images/6747-3-1327196300.png[/IMG]

[B]Hello @ all,[/B]

[B][COLOR=Red][SIZE=5]Black® Sexy Catsuit II HD,[/SIZE][/COLOR][/B]

is a textur HD-replacer at 2048x2048, that retextures Calientes BBE female body with one that  have a catsuit texture over it. As being an alternative nevernude version of Calientes CBBE nevenude mod It will replaces all female bodies. This mod will never show nudity even if you have installed a nude mod. With this mode you now can use the silly huge version of CBBE without nudity (that is not silly at all but the only version that makes sense :D). If you dont use a nude mode or use Calientes Nevernude version than underwear will be shown over the catsuit.

Best effects with [B]Calientes[/B] excellent [URL=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666]BBE mod [/URL], but this is not included and not required.

All pictures are made with Calientes CBBE mod and Bellas better Females activated, some with the Sillyhuge version, the others with the nevernude version enabled. In the pictures you also see my new Black® Sexy Underwear Mod with the nevernude version.

[B][SIZE=3]Install/Uninstall:[/SIZE][/B]

With Nexus Mod Manager or for manual install see included ReadMe.

[SIZE=\"3\"][B]Conflicts:[/B] [/SIZE]
This mod must be loaded/installed after Calientes CBBE or any other mod that replaces \"femalebody.dds\".
